{"tid":1321914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「劇情討論下」一班手無寸鐵既囚犯反擊軍隊","createTime":"2019-07-15T20:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T04:59:05.000Z","uid":152339,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e22409fe99cc0028f7b3e024b6a09a6e130fbe64","tid":1321914,"uid":152339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:10:02.000Z","msg":"好戲推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《叛將風雲》谷阿莫輕鬆講解版<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KZ0rDdH0Ju4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKZ0rDdH0Ju4&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=0f695a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KZ0rDdH0Ju4</a><br />\n<br />\n詳細內容版 (殘體字慎入)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fCxfLE3BgFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfCxfLE3BgFg&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=e54564e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fCxfLE3BgFg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懶人包主要內容<br />\n1. 引守衛無故暴打囚犯，等外界知道咩事<br />\n2. 二五仔放錯既情報俾敵方<br />\n3. 空城計<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">4. 佢地分散兵力，用計謀引班守衛到室內再封鎖晒啲門，反囚禁，出面嗰班就幾人一組，逐個趙佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n5. 斷水源，等佢哋用唔到水炮車。<br />\n6. 用餐廳鐵盆擋橡膠子彈。<br />\n7. 最後敵方增援，be water <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重點就係，佢地冇用到任何電子通訊裝備。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以！敵方完全唔知佢哋會有啲乜嘢行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打一齊討論下劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7f8b7381e01cf53c0b482d650a8518cd31132d","tid":1321914,"uid":152339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:11:42.000Z","msg":"有冇人未瞓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f21a23ba58d76f4d11dbfaf335ebae0bcc7bbd","tid":1321914,"uid":152339,"like":0,